Dialogue: At an end your rule is and not short enough it was I must say.

Script: YODA: (continuing) If so powerful you are why leave??
Dialogue: If so powerful you are why leave??

Script: DARTH SlDIOUS: You will not stop me. Darth Vader will become more powerful than either of us.
Dialogue: You will not stop me. Darth Vader will become more powerful than either of us.

Script: YODA: Faith in your new apprentice misplaced may be as is your faith in the dark side of the Force.
Dialogue: Faith in your new apprentice misplaced may be as is your faith in the dark side of the Force.

Script: ANAKIN: Don't make me destroy you Master. You're no match for the dark side.
Dialogue: Don't make me destroy you Master. You're no match for the dark side.

Script: OBI-WAN: I've heard that before Anakin . . . but I never thought I'd hear it from you.
Dialogue: I've heard that before Anakin . . . but I never thought I'd hear it from you.

Script: OBI-WAN: (continuing) The flaw of power is arrogance.
Dialogue: The flaw of power is arrogance.

Script: ANAKIN: You hesitate . . . the flaw of compassion.
Dialogue: You hesitate . . . the flaw of compassion.

Script: YODA: Destroy you I will just as Master Kenobi your apprentice will destroy.
Dialogue: Destroy you I will just as Master Kenobi your apprentice will destroy.

Script: YODA: Hurry. Careful timing we will need.
Dialogue: Hurry. Careful timing we will need.

Script: BAIL ORGANA: (in speeder) There aren't many troops on this side. Activate your homing beacon when you're ready.
Dialogue: There aren't many troops on this side. Activate your homing beacon when you're ready.

Script: CLONE COMMANDER THIRE: There is no sign of his body sir.
Dialogue: There is no sign of his body sir.

Script: MAS AMEDDA: Then he is not dead.
Dialogue: Then he is not dead.

Script: PALPATINE: Double your search.
Dialogue: Double your search.

Script: CLONE COMMANDER THIRE: Yes sir. Right away sir.
Dialogue: Yes sir. Right away sir.

Script: PALPATINE: (to Mas Amedda) Tell Captain Kagi to prepare my shuttle for immediate takeoff.
Dialogue: Tell Captain Kagi to prepare my shuttle for immediate takeoff.

Script: MAS AMEDDA: Yes Master.
Dialogue: Yes Master.

Script: PALPATINE: I sense Lord Vader is in danger.
Dialogue: I sense Lord Vader is in danger.

Script: YODA: Into exile I must go. Failed I have.
Dialogue: Into exile I must go. Failed I have.

Script: C-3PO: I am being careful. I've got a good hold on her but . . . I'm worried about my back. I hope it's able to hold up under this weight.
Dialogue: I am being careful. I've got a good hold on her but . . . I'm worried about my back. I hope it's able to hold up under this weight.

Script: OBI-WAN: I have failed you Anakin. I was never able to teach you to think.
Dialogue: I have failed you Anakin. I was never able to teach you to think.

Script: ANAKIN: I should have known the Jedi were plotting to take over . . .
Dialogue: I should have known the Jedi were plotting to take over . . .

Script: OBI-WAN: From the Sith!!! Anakin Chancellor Palpatine is evil.
Dialogue: From the Sith!!! Anakin Chancellor Palpatine is evil.

Script: ANAKIN: From the Jedi point of view! From my point of view the Jedi are evil.
Dialogue: From the Jedi point of view! From my point of view the Jedi are evil.

Script: OBI-WAN: Well then you are lost!
Dialogue: Well then you are lost!

Script: ANAKIN: This is the end for you My Master. I wish it were otherwise.
Dialogue: This is the end for you My Master. I wish it were otherwise.

Script: OBI-WAN: It's over Anakin. I have the high ground.
Dialogue: It's over Anakin. I have the high ground.

Script: ANAKIN: You underestimate my power!
Dialogue: You underestimate my power!

Script: OBI-WAN: Don't try it.
Dialogue: Don't try it.

Script: OBI-WAN: (continuing) . . . You were the Chosen One! It was said that you would destroy the Sith not join them. It was you who would bring balance to the Force not leave it in Darkness.
Dialogue: . . . You were the Chosen One! It was said that you would destroy the Sith not join them. It was you who would bring balance to the Force not leave it in Darkness.

Script: ANAKIN: I hate you!
Dialogue: I hate you!

Script: OBI-WAN: You were my brother Anakin. I loved you.
Dialogue: You were my brother Anakin. I loved you.

Script: C-3PO: Master Kenobi! We have Miss Padme on board. Please please hurry. We should leave this dreadful place.
Dialogue: Master Kenobi! We have Miss Padme on board. Please please hurry. We should leave this dreadful place.

Script: PADME: Obi-Wan? Is Anakin all right?
Dialogue: Obi-Wan? Is Anakin all right?

Script: DARTH SIDIOUS: Anakin! Anakin! There he is. He's still alive. Get a medical capsule immediately.
Dialogue: Anakin! Anakin! There he is. He's still alive. Get a medical capsule immediately.

Script: CLONE CAPTAIN: Yes sir. Right away.
Dialogue: Yes sir. Right away.

Script: YODA: Failed to stop the Sith Lord I have. Still much to learn there is ...
Dialogue: Failed to stop the Sith Lord I have. Still much to learn there is ...

Script: QUI -GON: (V.O.) Patience. You will have time. I did not. When I became one with the Force I made a great discovery. With my training you will be able to merge with the Force at will. Your physical self will fade away but you will still retain your consciousness. You will become more powerful than any Sith.
Dialogue: Patience. You will have time. I did not. When I became one with the Force I made a great discovery. With my training you will be able to merge with the Force at will. Your physical self will fade away but you will still retain your consciousness. You will become more powerful than any Sith.

Script: YODA: Eternal consciousness.
Dialogue: Eternal consciousness.

Script: QUI-GON: (V.O.) The ability to defy oblivion can be achieved but only for oneself. It was accomplished by a Shaman of the Whills. It is a state acquired through compassion not greed.
Dialogue: The ability to defy oblivion can be achieved but only for oneself. It was accomplished by a Shaman of the Whills. It is a state acquired through compassion not greed.

Script: YODA: . . . to become one with the Force and influence still have . . . A power greater than all it is.
Dialogue: . . . to become one with the Force and influence still have . . . A power greater than all it is.

Script: QUI-GON: (V.O.) You will learn to let go of everything. No attachment no thought of self. No physical self.
Dialogue: You will learn to let go of everything. No attachment no thought of self. No physical self.

Script: YODA: A great Jedi Master you have become Qui-Gon Jinn. Your apprentice I gratefully become.
Dialogue: A great Jedi Master you have become Qui-Gon Jinn. Your apprentice I gratefully become.

Script: BAIL ORGANA: Excuse me Master Yoda. Obi-Wan Kenobi has made contact.
Dialogue: Excuse me Master Yoda. Obi-Wan Kenobi has made contact.

Script: BAIL ORGANA: We'll take her to the medical center quickly.
Dialogue: We'll take her to the medical center quickly.

Script: MEDICAL DROID: Medically she is completely healthy. For reasons we can't explain we are losing her.
Dialogue: Medically she is completely healthy. For reasons we can't explain we are losing her.

Script: OBI-WAN: She's dying?
Dialogue: She's dying?

Script: MEDICAL DROID: We don't know why. She has lost the will to live. We need to operate quickly if we are to save the babies.
Dialogue: We don't know why. She has lost the will to live. We need to operate quickly if we are to save the babies.

Script: BAIL ORGANA: Babies??!!
Dialogue: Babies??!!

Script: MEDICAL DROID: She's carrying twins.
Dialogue: She's carrying twins.

Script: YODA: Save them we must. They are our last hope.
Dialogue: Save them we must. They are our last hope.

Script: C-3PO: It s some kind of reproductive process I think.
Dialogue: It s some kind of reproductive process I think.

Script: OBI-WAN: Don't give up Padme.
Dialogue: Don't give up Padme.

Script: MEDICAL DROID: It's a boy.
Dialogue: It's a boy.

Script: PADME: Luke . . .
Dialogue: Luke . . .

Script: MEDICAL DROID: ... and a girl.
Dialogue: ... and a girl.

Script: PADME: . . . Leia.
Dialogue: . . . Leia.

Script: OBI-WAN: You have twins Padme They need you . . . hang on.
Dialogue: You have twins Padme They need you . . . hang on.

Script: PADME: I can't . . .
Dialogue: I can't . . .

Script: OBI-WAN: Save your energy.
Dialogue: Save your energy.

Script: PADME: Obi-Wan . . . there . . . is good in him. I know there is ... still . . .
Dialogue: Obi-Wan . . . there . . . is good in him. I know there is ... still . . .

Script: MEDICAL DROID: My Lord the construction is finished ... he lives.
Dialogue: My Lord the construction is finished ... he lives.

Script: DARTH SIDIOUS: Good. Good.
Dialogue: Good. Good.

Script: DARTH SIDIOUS: (continuing) Lord Vader can you hear me?
Dialogue: Lord Vader can you hear me?

Script: DARTH VADER: Yes My Master.
Dialogue: Yes My Master.

Script: DARTH VADER: (continuing) Where is Padme? Is she safe is she all right?
Dialogue: Where is Padme? Is she safe is she all right?

Script: DARTH SIDIOUS: I'm afraid she died. ... it seems in your anger you killed her.
Dialogue: I'm afraid she died. ... it seems in your anger you killed her.

Script: DARTH VADER: I couldn't have! She was alive! I felt her! She was alive! It's impossible! No!!!
Dialogue: I couldn't have! She was alive! I felt her! She was alive! It's impossible! No!!!

Script: YODA: Pregnant she must still appear. Hidden safe the children must be kept.
Dialogue: Pregnant she must still appear. Hidden safe the children must be kept.

Script: OBI-WAN: We must take them somewhere the Sith will not sense their presence.
Dialogue: We must take them somewhere the Sith will not sense their presence.

Script: YODA: Split up they should be.
Dialogue: Split up they should be.

Script: BAIL ORGANA: My wife and I will take the girl. We've always talked of adopting a baby girl. She will be loved with us.
Dialogue: My wife and I will take the girl. We've always talked of adopting a baby girl. She will be loved with us.

Script: OBI-WAN: And what of the boy?
Dialogue: And what of the boy?

Script: YODA: To Tatooine. To his family send him.
Dialogue: To Tatooine. To his family send him.

Script: OBI-WAN: I will take the child and watch over him. Master Yoda do you think Anakin's twins will be able to defeat Darth Sidious?
Dialogue: I will take the child and watch over him. Master Yoda do you think Anakin's twins will be able to defeat Darth Sidious?

Script: YODA: Strong the Force runs in the Skywalker line. Hope we can . . . Done it is. Until the time is right disappear we will.
Dialogue: Strong the Force runs in the Skywalker line. Hope we can . . . Done it is. Until the time is right disappear we will.

Script: YODA: (continuing) Master Kenobi wait a moment. In your solitude on Tatooine training I have for you.
Dialogue: Master Kenobi wait a moment. In your solitude on Tatooine training I have for you.

Script: OBI-WAN: Training??
Dialogue: Training??

Script: YODA: An old friend has learned the path to immortality.
Dialogue: An old friend has learned the path to immortality.

Script: OBI-WAN: Who?
Dialogue: Who?

Script: YODA: One who has returned from the netherworld of the Force to train me . . . your old Master Qui-Gon Jinn.
Dialogue: One who has returned from the netherworld of the Force to train me . . . your old Master Qui-Gon Jinn.

Script: OBI-WAN: Qui-Gon? But how could he accomplish this?
Dialogue: Qui-Gon? But how could he accomplish this?

Script: YODA: The secret of the Ancient Order of the Whills he studied. How to commune with him. I will teach you.
Dialogue: The secret of the Ancient Order of the Whills he studied. How to commune with him. I will teach you.

Script: OBI-WAN: I will be able to talk with him?
Dialogue: I will be able to talk with him?

Script: YODA: How to join the Force he will train you. Your consciousness you will retain when one with the Force. Even your physical self perhaps.
Dialogue: How to join the Force he will train you. Your consciousness you will retain when one with the Force. Even your physical self perhaps.

Script: BAIL ORGANA: Captain Antilles.
Dialogue: Captain Antilles.

Script: CAPTAIN ANTILLES: Yes Your Highness.
Dialogue: Yes Your Highness.

Script: BAIL ORGANA: I'm placing these droids in your care. Treat them well. Clean them up. Have the Protocol Droid's mind wiped.
Dialogue: I'm placing these droids in your care. Treat them well. Clean them up. Have the Protocol Droid's mind wiped.

Script: C-3PO: Oh no.
Dialogue: Oh no.
